{"tid":1940441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己呢世都唔識再鍾意人","createTime":"2020-03-23T18:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T09:58:40.000Z","uid":315423,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"de930ea1346cfee40f5035f96cce3503040a63b6","tid":1940441,"uid":315423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"分咗手大半年<br />\n放係放低咗<br />\n但冇動力再主動重新相識一個人<br />\n諗到要由頭開始了解對方諗法 愛好 習慣 真系好攰<br />\n所有回憶堆疊到最後又係比時間沖走嘅產物<br />\n覺得以後都唔會再有一個咁有感覺嘅人出現然後一齊建立咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇動力啦"},{"pid":"70d5f5a44bbedd36ad40140898d02f30081815ca","tid":1940441,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:52:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2924e9f07ea3ab2259eae2199ee0594497599b64","tid":1940441,"uid":315423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70d5f5a44bbedd36ad40140898d02f30081815ca","tid":1940441,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:52:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:53:58.000Z","msg":"見到身邊啲人拍拖有時會羨慕 但又唔想拍拖 覺得自己冇能力handle一個人 好驚分手 好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bd91905ef43a6a4dac98d4f23936e7ca44d9a8","tid":1940441,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9af2d3d89921d601df81c07fc713db63a4adee64","tid":1940441,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2924e9f07ea3ab2259eae2199ee0594497599b64","tid":1940441,"uid":315423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70d5f5a44bbedd36ad40140898d02f30081815ca","tid":1940441,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":